org.apache.drill.exec.store.hive.readers

Class HiveTextRecordReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.store.AbstractRecordReader
      • org.apache.drill.exec.store.hive.readers.HiveDefaultRecordReader
        • org.apache.drill.exec.store.hive.readers.HiveTextRecordReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, RecordReader

    public class HiveTextRecordReader
extends HiveDefaultRecordReader
    Reading of Hive table stored in text format may require to skip few header/footer records. This class extends default reader to add the functionality.
